quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  43,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  43,1,Haa-Meeem
  43,2,kitaab roshan ki qasam
  43,3,ke hum ne is ko quran arabi banaya hai taakay tum samjhoo
  43,4,aur yeh barri kitaab ( yani looh mehfooz ) mein hamaray paas ( likhi hui aur ) barri fazeelat aur hikmat wali hai
  43,5,bhala is liye ke tum hadd se niklay hue log ho hum tum ko nasiyaat karne se baz rahen ge
  43,6,aur hum ne pehlay logon mein bhi bohat se paighambar beje they
  43,7,aur koi paighambar un ke paas nahi aata tha magar woh is se tamaskhur karte they
  43,8,to jo un mein sakht zor walay they un ko hum ne halaak kardiya aur aglay logon ki haalat guzar gayi
  43,9,aur agar tum un se pucho ke asmano aur zameen ko kis ne pedakiya hai to keh den ge ke un ko ghalib aur ilm walay ( khuda ) ne pedakiya hai
  43,10,jis ne tumahray liye zameen ko bichona banaya. aur is mein tumahray liye raste banaye taakay tum raah maloom karo
  43,11,aur jis ne aik andazay ke sath aasman se pani nazilkiya. phir hum ne is se shehar murda ko zindahkiya. isi terhan tum zameen se nikalay jao ge
  43,12,aur jis ne tamam qisam ke hewanat peda kiye aur tumahray liye kashtiyan aur charpaye banaye jin par tum sawaar hotay ho
  43,13,taakay tum un ki peeth par charh betho aur jab is par baith jao phir apne perwar-digaar ke ahsaan ko yaad karo aur kaho ke woh ( zaat ) pak hai jis ne is ko hamaray zair farmaan kar diya aur hum mein taaqat nah thi ke is ko bas mein kar lete
  43,14,aur hum apne perwar-digaar ki taraf lout kar jaane walay hain
  43,15,aur unhon ne is ke bundon mein se is ke liye aulaad muqarrar ki. be shak ensaan Sarih nashukara hai
  43,16,kiya is ne apni makhloqaat mein se khud to betiyan len aur tum ko chunn kar betay diye
  43,17,halaank jab un mein se kisi ko is cheez ki khushkhabri di jati hai jo unhon ne khuda ke liye bayan ki hai to is ka munh siyah hojata aur woh gham se bhar jata hai
  43,18,kiya woh jo zewar mein parwarish paye aur jhagrre ke waqt baat nah kar sakay ( khuda ki ) beti hosakti hai ?
  43,19,aur unhon ne firshton ko ke woh bhi khuda ke bande hain ( khuda ki ) betiyan muqarrarkiya.kiya yeh un ki paidaiesh ke waqt haazir they anqareeb un ki shahadat likh li jaye gi aur un se bazprs ki jaye gi
  43,20,aur kehte hain agar khuda chahta to hum un ko nah pujte. un ko is ka kuch ilm nahi. yeh to sirf atklin dora rahay hain
  43,21,ya hum ne un ko is se pehlay koi kitaab di thi to yeh is se sanad pakarte hain
  43,22,balkay kehnay lagey ke hum ne apne baap dada ko aik raste par paaya hai aur hum unhi ke qadam bqdm chal rahay hain
  43,23,aur isi terhan hum ne tum se pehlay kisi bastii mein koi hadaayat karne wala nahi bheja magar wahan ke khushaal logon ne kaha ke hum ne apne baap dada ko aik raah par paaya aur hum qadam bqdm un hi ke peechay chaltay hain
  43,24,paighambar ne kaha agarchay mein tumahray paas aisa ( deen ) lau ke jis raste par tum ne apne baap dada ko paaya woh is se kahin seedha rasta dekhata hai kehnay lagey ke jo ( deen ) tum day kar beje gay ho hum is ko nahi mantay
  43,25,to hum ne un se intiqam liya so dekh lau ke jhutlanay walon ka injaam kaisa howa
  43,26,aur jab ibrahim ne apne baap aur apni qoum ke logon se kaha ke jin cheezon ko tum pujte ho mein un se bezaar hon
  43,27,haan jis ne mujh ko pedakiya wohi mujhe seedha rasta dukhaay ga
  43,28,aur yahi baat apni aulaad mein peechay chore gay taakay woh ( khuda ki taraf ) rujoo karen
  43,29,baat yeh hai ke mein un kufar ko aur un ke baap dada ko mtmta karta raha yahan taq ke un ke paas haq aur saaf saaf bayan karne wala paighambar aa pouncha
  43,30,aur jab un ke paas haq ( yani quran ) aaya to kehnay lagey ke yeh to jaadoo hai aur hum is ko nahi mantay
  43,31,aur ( yeh bhi ) kehnay lagey ke yeh quran un dono bustiyon ( yani mukkay aur Taif ) mein se kisi barray aadmi par kyun nazil nahkiya gaya ?
  43,32,kiya yeh log tumahray perwar-digaar ki rehmat ko banttay hain? hum ne un mein un ki maeeshat ko duniya ki zindagi mein taqseem kardiya aur aik ke dosray par darjay buland kiye taakay aik dosray se khidmat le aur jo kuch yeh jama karte hain tumahray perwar-digaar ki rehmat is se kahin behtar hai
  43,33,aur agar yeh khayaal nah hota ke sab log aik hi jamaat ho jaien ge to jo log khuda se inkaar karte hain hum un ke gharon ki chhatain chandi ki bana dete aur seedhiyan ( bhi ) jin par woh charhtay hain
  43,34,aur un ke gharon ke darwazay bhi aur takhat bhi jin par takiya lagatay hain
  43,35,aur ( khoob ) Tajammal vaaraysh ( kardete ) aur yeh sab duniya ki zindagi ka thora sa samaan hai. aur akhirat tumahray perwar-digaar ke haan parhaiz garon ke liye hai
  43,36,aur jo koi khuda ki yaad se ankhen band karkay ( yani taghaful kere ) hum is par aik shetan muqarrar kardete hain to woh is ka saathi hojata hai
  43,37,aur yeh ( shetan ) un ko raste se roktay rehtay hain aur woh samajte hain ke seedhay raste par hain
  43,38,yahan taq ke jab hamaray paas aeye ga to kahe ga ke ae kash mujh mein aur tujh mein mashriq o maghrib ka faasla hota to bura saathi hai
  43,39,aur jab tum zulm karte rahay to aaj tumhe yeh baat faida nahi day sakti ke tum ( sab ) azaab mein shareek ho
  43,40,kiya tum behray ko suna satke ho ya andhay ko rasta dikha satke ho aur jo Sarih gumraahi mein ho ( usay raah par laskte ho )
  43,41,agar hum tum ko ( wafaat day kar ) utha len to un logon se to hum intiqam le kar rahen ge
  43,42,ya ( tumhari zindagi hi mein ) tumhe woh ( azaab ) dikha den ge jin ka hum ne un se wadakiya hai hum un par qaboo rakhtay hain
  43,43,pas tumhari taraf jo wahi ki gayi hai is ko mazboot pakdae raho. be shak tum seedhay raste par ho
  43,44,aur yeh ( quran ) tumahray liye aur tumhari qoum ke liye nasiyaat hai aur ( logo ) tum se anqareeb prssh hogi
  43,45,aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) jo apne paighambar hum ne tum se pehlay beje hain un se daryaft karlo.kiya hum ne ( khuday-e ) rehman ke siwa aur mabood banaye they ke un ki ibadat ki jaye
  43,46,aur hum ne moose ko apni nishanain day kar firaon aur is ke drbaryon ki taraf bheja to unhon ne kaha ke mein perwar-digaar aalam ka bheja howa hon
  43,47,jab woh un ke paas hamari nishanain le kar aeye to woh nshanyon se hansi karne lagey
  43,48,aur jo nishani hum un ko dikhata they woh doosri se barri hoti thi aur hum ne un ko azaab mein pakar liya taakay baz ayen
  43,49,aur kehnay lagey ke ae jadugar is ehad ke mutabiq jo tairay perwar-digaar ne tujh se kar rakha hai is se dua kar be shak hum hadaayat yab ho jayen ge
  43,50,so jab hum ne un se azaab ko daur kardiya to woh ehad shikni karne lagey
  43,51,aur firaon ne apni qoum se pukaar kar kaha ke ae qoumkiya misar ki hukoomat mere haath mein nahi hai. aur yeh nehrain jo mere ( mehloon ke ) neechay beh rahi hain ( meri nahi hain )kiya tum dekhte nahi
  43,52,be shak mein is shakhs se jo kuch izzat nahi rakhta aur saaf guftagu bhi nahi karsaktha kahin behtar hon
  43,53,to is par sonay ke kangon kyun nah utaray gay ya ( yeh hota ke ) farishtay jama ho kar is ke sath atay
  43,54,gharz is ne apni qoum ki aqal maar di. aur unhon ne is ki baat maan li. be shak woh nafarman log they
  43,55,jab unhon ne hum ko khafakiya to hum ne un se intiqam le kar aur un sab ko duubo kar chorra
  43,56,aur un ko gay guzray kardiya aur pichlon ke liye Ibrat bana diya
  43,57,aur jab maryam ke betay ( eesa ) ka haal bayankiya gaya to tumhari qoum ke log is se Chala uthay
  43,58,aur kehnay lagey ke bhala hamaray mabood achay hain ya eesa? unhon ne eesa ki jo misaal bayan ki hai to sirf jhagrnay ko. haqeeqat yeh hai yeh log hain hi jhagralu
  43,59,woh to hamaray aisay bande they jin par hum ne fazlkiya aur bani Israel ke liye un ko ( apni qudrat ka ) namona bana diya
  43,60,aur agar hum chahtay to tum mein se farishtay bana dete jo tumhari jagah zameen mein rehtay
  43,61,aur woh qayamat ki nishani hain. to ( keh do ke logo ) is mein shak nah karo aur mere peechay chalo. yahi seedha rasta hai
  43,62,aur ( kahin ) shetan tum ko ( is se ) rok nah day. woh to tumhara ا aylaniya dushman hai
  43,63,aur jab eesa nishanain le kar aeye to kehnay lagey ke mein tumahray paas danai ( ki kitaab ) le kar aaya hon. neez is liye ke baaz baatein jin mein tum ikhtilaaf kar rahay ho tum ko samgha dun. to khuda se daro aur mera kaha manu
  43,64,kuch shak nahi ke khuda hi mera aur tumhara perwar-digaar hai pas isi ki ibadat karo. yahi seedha rasta hai
  43,65,phir kitney firqay un mein se phatt gay. so jo log zalim hain un ki dard dainay walay din ke azaab se kharabi hai
  43,66,yeh sirf is baat ke munhtazir hain ke qayamat un par nagahan aa maujood ho aur un ko khabar taq nah ho
  43,67,( jo aapas mein ) dost ( hain ) is roz aik dosray ke dushman hon ge. magar parhaizgaar ( ke baahum dost hi rahen ge )
  43,68,mere Bandoo aaj tumhe nah kuch khauf hai aur nah tum ghumnaak hogay
  43,69,jo log hamari aayton par imaan laaye aur farmanbardar hogaye
  43,70,( un se kaha jaye ga ) ke tum aur tumhari biwiyan izzat ( vahtram ) ke sath bahisht mein daakhil hojao
  43,71,un par sonay ki prchon aur peyaalon ka daur chalay ga. aur wahan jo jee chahay aur jo aankhon ko acha lagey ( mojood hoga ) aur ( ae ahal jannat ) tum is mein hamesha raho ge
  43,72,aur yeh jannat jis ke tum maalik kar diye gay ho tumahray aamaal ka sila hai
  43,73,wahan tumahray liye bohat se meway hain jin ko tum khao ge
  43,74,( aur kufar ) gunehgaar hamesha dozakh ke azaab mein rahen ge
  43,75,jo un se halka nahkiya jaye ga aur woh is mein na ummid ho kar parre rahen ge
  43,76,aur hum ne un par zulm nahikiya. balkay wohi ( apne aap par ) zulm karte they
  43,77,aur pukaarain ge ke ae maalik tumhara perwar-digaar hamein mout day day. woh kahe ga ke tum hamesha ( isi haalat mein ) raho ge
  43,78,hum tumahray paas haq le kar aeye hain lekin tum aksar haq se nakhush hotay rahay
  43,79,kiya unhon ne koi baat thehra rakhi hai to hum bhi kuch thehranay walay hain
  43,80,kiya yeh log yeh khayaal karte hain ke hum un ki posheeda baton aur sargoshiyon ko suntay nahi? haan haan ( sab suntay hain ) aur hamaray farishtay un ke paas ( un ki sab baatein ) likh letay hain
  43,81,keh do ke agar khuda ke aulaad ho to mein ( sab se ) pehlay ( is ki ) ibadat karne wala hon
  43,82,yeh jo kuch bayan karte hain asmano aur zameen ka maalik ( aur ) arsh ka maalik is se pak hai
  43,83,to un ko buk buk karne aur khailnay do. yahan taq ke jis din ka un se wadakiya jata hai is ko dekh len
  43,84,aur wohi ( aik ) asmano mein mabood hai aur ( wohi ) zameen mein mabood hai. aur woh Dana ( aur ) ilm wala hai
  43,85,aur woh bohat babarkat hai jis ke liye asmano aur zameen ki aur jo kuch un dono mein hai sab ki badshahat hai. aur isi ko qayamat ka ilm hai aur isi ki taraf tum lout kar jao ge
  43,86,aur jin ko yeh log khuda ke siwa pkarte hain woh sifarish ka kuch ikhtiyar nahi rakhtay. haan jo ilm ویقین ke sath haq ki gawahi den ( woh sifarish kar saktay hain )
  43,87,aur agar tum un se pucho ke un ko kis ne pedakiya hai to keh den ge ke khuda ne. to phir yeh kahan behke phirtay hain ?
  43,88,aur ( bsaavqat ) paighambar kaha karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar yeh aisay log hain ke imaan nahi laatay
  43,89,to un se munh phair lau aur salam keh do. un ko anqareeb ( injaam ) maloom hojaye ga
